            <div style="background: #1c2230; color: #f0f0f5; max-width: 78%; padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 18px 18px 18px 4px; font-size: 14px; align-self: flex-start; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 180, 173, 0.15);">今日 REINS デイリーレポート</div>
            <div style="background: #1d4ed8; color: #fff; max-width: 78%; padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 18px 18px 4px 18px; font-size: 14px; align-self: flex-end;">查一下目黒</div>
